title: Madlax O.S.T. 1 mp3
description:
The Original Soundtrack of the Madlax anime, converted from .ogg to .mp3 so that it'll work with iTunes. 

PS: I'm not likely to be a very good uploader, seeing as I don't have anything as fancy as a dedicated server or a very fast internet connection, but pauses aside I'm not planning to stop seeding this - ever - so just be patient (or find the torrent I got the .oggs off and convert it yourself). 

PPS: This is my first torrent (second will come in 2 minutes or so) so I might be mistaken about the PS. Comments are welcome.
